사진 찍은 날짜: 2008년 10월 04일 오후 8:54</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SHAPECOMPONENT CurHeight="22303" CurWidth="30862" GroupLevel="0" HorzFlip="false" InstID="1018710363" OriHeight="27642" OriWidth="38249" VertFlip="false" XPos="-7387" YPos="-2466"><ROTATIONINFO Angle="0" CenterX="15431" CenterY="11151"/><RENDERINGINFO><TRANSMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="-7387.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="-2466.00000"/><SCAMATRIX E1="0.80687" E2="0.00000" E3="7387.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="0.80685" E6="2466.00000"/><ROTMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/></RENDERINGINFO></SHAPECOMPONENT><IMAGERECT X0="0" X1="38249" X2="38249" X3="0" Y0="0" Y1="0" Y2="27642" Y3="27642"/><IMAGECLIP Bottom="24960" Left="0" Right="34560" Top="0"/><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0"/><IMAGE Alpha="0" BinItem="2" Bright="0" Contrast="0" Effect="RealPic"/><EFFECTS/></PICTURE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>As can be seen the Goodwin model can generate endogenous fluctuations in economic activity without relying on extraneous assumptions of outside shocks, whether on the demand or supply side.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P></SECTION></BODY><TAIL><BINDATASTORAGE><BINDATA Encoding="Base64" Id="1" Size="22127">/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQEAYABgAAD/2wBDAAMCAgMCAgMDAwMEAwMEBQgFBQQEBQoHBwYIDAoM
